@startuml Login_Flow
actor User
participant "Login Screen" as UI
participant "Security Filter" as Sec
participant "CustomerDetailsService" as CDS
database "MySQL" as DB

User -> UI: Enter Email/Pass
UI -> Sec: POST /api/auth/login
Sec -> CDS: loadUserByUsername(email)
CDS -> DB: SELECT * FROM customers WHERE email=?
DB --> CDS: UserData + HashedPass
CDS --> Sec: UserDetails
Sec -> Sec: Match Password (BCrypt)
Sec --> UI: 200 OK + Auth Cookie/Token
UI -> User: Show Dashboard
@enduml
